# 5. 今日は、高校生として

Haruka: Alright everyone, see you next time. Remember to keep this a secret, okay?
Elementary Schooler on a Field Trip: Okay! We promise! Take care, Haruka!
Haruka: Phew, looks like they were satisfied.
Haruka: (But that took much longer than I expected. I don't want to keep Hoshino and the others waiting, so I'd better hurry.)
Haruka: (We were all supposed to go around as a group, but we ended up separating. I feel bad.)
Haruka: First things first, I need to go meet up with them as soon as I can.
Haruka: (Where could they be?)
Haruka: (They just replied to my message saying they were in this shop, but...)
???: Oh! There she is! Hey!
Haruka: Tenma! Everyone! I'm so sorry for making you wait...
Haruka: Hm? What are you all doing?
Saki: Heh heh heh...
Saki: Ta-da! We picked out some stuff that will create the perfect disguise for you, Haruka!
Haruka: What?
Sonoda: We were just talking about what a famous person would wear and what would suit you, and ended up trying on a bunch of stuff.
Ichika: A disguise that makes you look famous would defeat the purpose, though.
Inoue: Oh, but don't worry! We didn't pick anything like that!
Haruka: Everyone...
Saki: This way you'll be able to walk around without being interrupted!
Haruka: Oh...
Haruka: You're right. Sorry for the trouble.
Saki: Ah! No, no, that's not what I meant!
Saki: I just want to enjoy today's trip as much as possible with you!
Saki: I mean, we got to be in the same group!
Haruka: Tenma...
Ichika: It's not just Saki. We all feel the same.
Ichika: I know that you really care about your fans, and perhaps it's selfish of us to feel this way.
Ichika: But we really want to make the most of this field trip and have fun with you.
Inoue: We were thinking about what we can do to help, and the only thing we came up with was picking out some stuff for a disguise...
Haruka: (Everyone...)
Miku: It's a special occasion, so please enjoy your field trip as any high school students would!
Haruka: (That's right... I came here to have fun as any regular student would.)
Haruka: (I made plans with everyone for that purpose. And yet... I wasn't following through.)
Haruka: Thank you, everyone. That makes me happy.
Haruka: Yes, I do think a lot about my fans and want to give back what I can for their ongoing support.
Haruka: But even so, I also really want to have fun with all of you. And that is the truth.
Haruka: So, I think I'll take you up on your offer and let myself fully enjoy this trip!
Saki: Yeah! Let's all have a great time!
Haruka: Going back to the disguise, what items have you picked out?
Saki: Well, we had a hard time picking out a hat, but what do you think of this flat cap? I think this would totally suit you♪
Haruka: Oh, that's nice. It has a simple design and I can probably wear this on any regular day too.
Sonoda: Yeah, it looks really good on you!
Ichika: What about these sunglasses? I thought they would look really cool on you.
Haruka: I think I'll pass on those. They're a little too flashy and might actually attract more attention.
Ichika: Really?
Inoue: See? I told you those were too flashy!
Ichika: But I thought they'd look really good on her...
Saki: Glad that we were able to find something good!
Sonoda: Yeah! It really suits you, Kiritani!
Ichika: I didn't realize that you could look so different just by wearing a hat. I don't think anyone will notice now.
Haruka: Really? That's a relief. Now I should be fine to relax and just enjoy walking around.
Haruka: So, what should we do next? Did you want to stay here for a little longer?
Saki: We managed to get the perfect disguise for you and I got my souvenirs, so I'm pretty satisfied!
Ichika: Me too. We finished up earlier than we planned, but shall we head out anyway?
Inoue: Okay!
Passerby: Hey, did you see? Apparently Haruka Kiritani was here today.
Passerby: Huh? Haruka Kiritani? You mean THE Haruka Kiritani?
Passerby: Yup! She's trending on social media right now. Quite a few people are saying they saw her, so I think it's legit!
Haruka: (Oh no... They're talking about me.)
Ichika: Did people find out from hearing those kids before?
Haruka: I think so... But it should be fine because of the hat you all picked out for me.
Saki: Oh! They're coming this way!
Passerby: Apparently, she's really pretty and slim in person! I wish I could see her!
Passerby: What if she's nearby?! If we bump into her, let's try asking for a photo!
Haruka: ...
Everyone: ...
Haruka: Looks like they left...
Ichika & Saki: *Sigh*
Inoue: I was so anxious that they were going to recognize you!
Ichika: Me too... My heart was racing.
Sonoda: I know, right?! My palms are so sweaty!
Saki: Hehehe. Operation Disguise was... A. Big. Success♪
Haruka: Hehe. Yes, it was.
